videos.headline: Arkansas converts quick pass into 38-yard TD
videos.description: Austin Allen connects with Deon Stewart, who gets a block and takes it for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arkansas converts quick pass into 38-yard TD) 2017/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rogers throws red zone INT
videos.description: New Mexico State QB Tyler Rogers throws an interception in the end zone for his first turnover of the game.

videos.headline: Whaley's TD extends Arkansas' lead
videos.description: Arkansas RB Devwah Whaley breaks out to the right for a three-yard touchdown in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Allen connects with Nance for TD
videos.description: Arkansas QB Austin Allen finds WR Jonathan Nance in the end zone for a 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: New Mexico St. scores on 1-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Quarterback Tyler Rogers keeps the ball on an option play as he scores New Mexico States first touchdown of the day against Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (New Mexico St. scores on 1-yard rushing TD) 2017/09/30

videos.headline: Hayden punches it in for 2-yard Arkansas TD
videos.description: Chase Hayden lowers his pads and breaks the plane of the end zone for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hayden punches it in for 2-yard Arkansas TD) 2017/09/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rogers's TD pass cuts into the Razorbacks' lead
videos.description: Tyler Rogers connects with OJ Clark for a 9-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rogers's TD pass cuts into the Razorbacks' lead) 2017/09/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nance's second TD catch gives Razorbacks big lead
videos.description: Arkansas QB Austin Allen finds WR Jonathan Nance in the end zone to give the Razorbacks a 35-17 lead over New Mexico State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nance’s second TD catch gives Razorbacks big lead) 2017/09/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Scott makes nice leaping grab for New Mexico State TD
videos.description: Tyler Rogers fires it to Jaleel Scott, who hauls in a 36-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Scott makes nice leaping grab for New Mexico State TD) 2017/09/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bielema: Arkansas took a 'step forward' against NMSU
videos.description: Bret Bielema discusses QB Austin Allen's 3-touchdown performance and looks ahead to facing South Carolina.
